properties.name: doyto.query.config.map-camel-case-to-underscore
properties.description: True to map camelCase to under_score. Default: false.

properties.name: doyto.query.config.ignore-cache-exception
properties.description: Ignore cache operation exception, e.g. timeout. Default: true.

properties.name: doyto.query.config.start-page-number-from-one
properties.description: Set start page number to 1. Default: true. Since 0.3.0.

properties.name: doyto.query.config.table-format
properties.description: Table format for domain. Default: t_%s. Since 0.3.1.

properties.name: doyto.query.config.join-table-format
properties.description: Join table format for multiple tables query. Default: j_%s_and_%s. Since 0.3.1.
